Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.35,0:00:03.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龐大的力量蘊於其身
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.04,0:00:06.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有烙印了宿命的人才有權享受
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.80,0:00:08.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無盡的快感
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.80,0:00:10.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後 毀滅
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.81,0:00:11.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Witch Blade
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.34,0:00:15.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在 一名女性覺醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.67,0:01:59.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎啦 已經到極限了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.61,0:02:00.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無聊的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.96,0:02:03.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本以為還能再打一會兒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.00,0:02:05.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡的話
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.34,0:02:09.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒開始呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.75,0:02:14.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不認真點的話 我的激情是難以燃燒的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.03,0:02:19.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我就對你… 認·真·點
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.26,0:02:31.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這還不錯   
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.52,0:02:35.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有點喜歡上你了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.08,0:02:40.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.03,0:02:58.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好強呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.97,0:03:02.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕 太用力了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.06,0:03:04.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 快給我站起來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.75,0:03:07.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.79,0:03:08.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快給我站起來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.49,0:03:23.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情況一面倒了 那個傢伙會就這麼死了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.87,0:03:25.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在笑著嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.40,0:03:28.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,志織
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.88,0:03:37.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.13,0:03:41.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中途就結束了 也太差勁了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.30,0:03:44.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正·胸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.80,0:03:51.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.88,0:03:55.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按住 快開車 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.29,0:03:56.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.30,0:04:03.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難得的獵物  別想逃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.15,0:04:07.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,志織 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.63,0:04:25.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可是特大素材呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.70,0:04:38.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.31,0:04:40.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊情況怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.17,0:04:42.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追上來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.64,0:04:44.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以這輛車的裝甲的話 應該可以撐一會
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.83,0:04:45.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 一定要撐下去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.67,0:04:47.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.13,0:04:51.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.05,0:04:59.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生什麼事了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.22,0:05:00.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼  
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.87,0:05:04.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼大不了的事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.82,0:05:09.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是 得回公司一趟 就到這吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.20,0:05:14.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎\N相隔這麼長時間還能見到你 真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.22,0:05:15.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彼此
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.83,0:05:17.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就先告辭了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.60,0:05:27.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我祈禱著 六年前的慘劇不會再重演
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.50,0:05:33.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有什麼我們能幫上的 無論何時 任何事都…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.90,0:05:37.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是個狡猾的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.27,0:05:42.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才Lady她們襲擊雅音的事 不可能不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.54,0:05:46.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我們說過不知道WitchBlade呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.38,0:05:48.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要抱怨了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.54,0:05:52.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要避免NswF和導示的正面對立 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.47,0:05:54.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是公司的方針
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.10,0:05:56.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話雖如此
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.82,0:05:59.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現場怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.67,0:06:03.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打算使用A號緊急撤退路線
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.75,0:06:05.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就得躲到實驗室裡了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.72,0:06:06.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.02,0:06:10.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這回還是盡力躲到和導示沒有關係的地方比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.34,0:06:12.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的遊艇能用嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.32,0:06:16.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知局長什麼時候回去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.84,0:06:19.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直跟著來了 就在那
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.71,0:06:25.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 就在那匯合 快點
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.09,0:06:26.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.96,0:06:28.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在孤月大橋那
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.28,0:06:31.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 在上面出現了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.42,0:06:35.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把她甩下去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.40,0:06:36.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.56,0:06:40.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真難纏 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.79,0:06:46.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是現在
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.40,0:06:59.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.21,0:07:01.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕不上匯合的時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.93,0:07:02.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.26,0:07:09.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.93,0:07:12.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這回可跑不掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.19,0:07:17.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,9..8..7..6..5
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.30,0:07:22.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,4..3..2..1..0
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.75,0:07:32.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 素材又來了… 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.89,0:07:34.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之是那輛卡車…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.23,0:07:37.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,車這方面讓別組回收
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.40,0:07:38.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.91,0:07:41.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,運送完成了 局長
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.65,0:07:42.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 出發
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.41,0:07:50.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.80,0:07:54.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,志織 振作一點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.21,0:08:00.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,志織 還認識我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.11,0:08:05.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.37,0:08:14.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切 如果沒有煙的話就能…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.71,0:08:21.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是到底有什麼內幕\h大型卡車之後又是遊艇 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.59,0:08:23.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正·胸這個傢伙到底…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.30,0:08:27.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被打得很重啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.32,0:08:30.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,治療拜託你了 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.39,0:08:33.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暫時還是在海上比較安全
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.43,0:08:35.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.01,0:08:59.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.46,0:09:01.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.67,0:09:04.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 老師有點太誇張了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.64,0:09:07.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是有點忘我 做過了頭
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.64,0:09:10.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 可是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.45,0:09:12.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想趁此機會好好地研究一下  
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.11,0:09:14.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很珍貴的數據呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.09,0:09:18.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是怎麼能讓老師自己來研究呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.65,0:09:30.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 請好好地休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.41,0:09:32.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.73,0:09:45.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就 請轉到檢查室
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.36,0:09:48.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以我的名字可優先執行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.69,0:09:49.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.38,0:10:59.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24}出去工作去了 要看家呀 拜託了 媽媽 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.98,0:11:04.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 媽媽在努力工作呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.98,0:11:06.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要努力
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.02,0:11:08.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.45,0:11:14.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 又不是沒有房間
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.98,0:11:16.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼在這種地方睡覺
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.72,0:11:21.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 起來了 小子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.44,0:11:24.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可不是你的床呀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.94,0:11:27.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正·胸回來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.73,0:11:29.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在等那個人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.79,0:11:32.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喜歡的是那種類型呀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.45,0:11:34.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.16,0:11:37.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是 和工作有關
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.68,0:11:38.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼呀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.54,0:11:40.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…還不能說
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.49,0:11:43.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正肯定是假素材
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.36,0:11:44.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 你等著瞧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.08,0:11:47.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 大家
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.63,0:11:49.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的臉色也不好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.73,0:11:51.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了這樣的大家 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.57,0:11:54.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨穗子為我們準備了美味的早餐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.67,0:11:55.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.00,0:11:59.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為努力做多了很多
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.45,0:12:01.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不錯 不錯…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.89,0:12:03.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜梅
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.42,0:12:05.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼簡單的早餐是不行 不行的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.66,0:12:07.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要把這個吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.65,0:12:10.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 長先生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.29,0:12:12.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大姐頭 以後多多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.60,0:12:18.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲 醒著嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.33,0:12:20.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給 請用
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.08,0:12:21.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.90,0:12:22.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.09,0:12:25.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你媽媽 昨晚到現在都沒回來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.21,0:12:27.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 有工作
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.73,0:12:28.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作? 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.47,0:12:31.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道是什麼工作嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.86,0:12:35.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是個綜合公司哦 在很大的一個公司幫忙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.64,0:12:39.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說的很大的公司 公司名呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.66,0:12:41.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼總問有關媽媽的事呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.13,0:12:44.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這有點… 以後再…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.41,0:12:48.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斗澤 不要總粘著梨穗子呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.51,0:12:50.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想想年紀大一點的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.90,0:12:52.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可不想被長先生這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.11,0:12:55.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是朋友 對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.20,0:12:55.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.95,0:12:57.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 梨穗子 一起吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.92,0:12:58.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.58,0:12:59.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.51,0:13:04.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什麼素材 我不知道 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.73,0:13:07.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 不要把小孩捲進去哦 行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.82,0:13:09.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 知道了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.62,0:13:11.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好香啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.66,0:13:15.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個…很好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.47,0:13:19.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎  以後我再試著放些芥末進去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.22,0:13:21.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨穗子的廚藝很好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.88,0:13:23.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.71,0:13:27.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能再年輕六十歲的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.71,0:13:32.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一下子吃那麼多 沒事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.62,0:13:35.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為肚子餓了啊 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.69,0:13:37.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使用過WitchBlade之後 一直是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.30,0:13:42.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 和昨晚就要死的狀態完全不相稱的吃相呀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.06,0:13:44.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙 怎麼不敲門
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.69,0:13:47.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種恢復力真是驚人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.46,0:13:50.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然是WitchBlade的能力之一 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.64,0:13:51.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可還是在意想之外
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.12,0:13:52.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.62,0:14:00.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做什麼呢你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.21,0:14:01.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.57,0:14:04.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回復能力確實上升了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.43,0:14:06.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把數據送到實驗室就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.12,0:14:07.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.94,0:14:10.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 我可不是倉鼠啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.68,0:14:12.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倉鼠?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.24,0:14:16.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要說小白鼠嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.05,0:14:19.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎樣 我要回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.51,0:14:20.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 大家辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.34,0:14:22.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看看窗外吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.99,0:14:23.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯? 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.52,0:14:30.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.53,0:14:34.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為開了一晚上 所以現在在離岸很遠的海面上 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.43,0:14:38.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然現在正開向岸邊 不過要花些時間哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.25,0:14:41.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會 什麼都沒向梨穗子說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.43,0:14:43.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打電話不就行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.87,0:14:46.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這之前把繃帶換下來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.13,0:14:49.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請脫下衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.24,0:14:49.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.26,0:14:52.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我看看傷口的癒合情況
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.05,0:14:55.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道 這是你…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.31,0:14:59.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必擔心 因為我看護士的資格
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.60,0:15:00.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.92,0:15:06.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道… 你不會也一起看了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.07,0:15:10.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪個好啊  想讓我看嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.21,0:15:12.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開什麼玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.14,0:15:13.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雅音小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.21,0:15:17.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滾出去 色鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.15,0:15:20.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,H…!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.05,0:15:27.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好奇怪呀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.16,0:15:31.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這點小傷 平常的話一會兒就癒合了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.08,0:15:33.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是不疼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.57,0:15:35.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.12,0:15:37.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.56,0:15:42.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狀況確實有些不對
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.24,0:15:44.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是到底…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.98,0:16:07.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.07,0:16:10.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在剛才 清掃員發現的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.89,0:16:12.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請聯繫一下屍體處理班  
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.06,0:16:14.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這引起大騷亂的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.27,0:16:16.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會讓教父不高興的  
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.72,0:16:18.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們來處理吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.61,0:16:20.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.36,0:16:23.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師 是X-CON嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.63,0:16:24.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有這種可能
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.56,0:16:26.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.20,0:16:27.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不要動
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.64,0:16:28.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.49,0:16:29.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是命令哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.96,0:16:32.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在檢查結果出來之前 什麼也不要做
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.23,0:16:33.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.93,0:16:37.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果X-CON在這麼近的話 應該會感覺到的 可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.95,0:16:39.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.78,0:16:48.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了來了 天羽…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.42,0:16:50.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.26,0:16:52.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.70,0:16:55.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有長先生他們在 一點也不寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.47,0:16:58.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽 沒事吧 好好吃飯了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.31,0:17:01.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 雖然沒有梨穗子做的飯好吃…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.04,0:17:04.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看樣子工作要再花些時間  
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.22,0:17:07.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼事的話就跟長先生說哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.36,0:17:10.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.40,0:17:12.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在努力工作哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.88,0:17:15.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係的 拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.70,0:17:28.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從這邊看 還不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.18,0:17:31.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.10,0:17:35.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.98,0:17:40.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海風對頭髮不好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.16,0:17:41.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.00,0:17:44.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真是個奇怪的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.56,0:17:49.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變成了WitchBlade之後 還和不明物體戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.58,0:17:53.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明知道那是以生命為賭注的戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.72,0:17:56.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有哭 也不害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.99,0:18:01.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這難道是沒有理解狀況的能力嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.88,0:18:03.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在說什麼呀你 真沒禮貌
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.46,0:18:05.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些事 我也會想的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.31,0:18:08.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我會遇到這種事之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.30,0:18:13.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼大家都想得到WitchBlade之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.43,0:18:13.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那之後呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.87,0:18:19.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是… 沒辦法嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.29,0:18:21.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.61,0:18:23.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法呀 變成這樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.51,0:18:27.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與此相比好好地撫養梨穗子才是最重要的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.67,0:18:31.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.59,0:18:34.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.37,0:18:43.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是? 什麼呀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.44,0:18:46.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.93,0:18:50.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來 這次有工傷保險嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.90,0:18:51.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工傷保險?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.36,0:18:56.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是工作中受的傷啊 不是有什麼津貼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.62,0:19:01.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 想逃避嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.41,0:19:02.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別想矇混過去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.58,0:19:06.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 果然只是個笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.53,0:19:10.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼! 你只是個小氣鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.08,0:19:11.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小氣 小氣…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.67,0:19:17.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只看這個的話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.74,0:19:20.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟UFO和宇宙人的照片 沒兩樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.93,0:19:23.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是不慎重地調查的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.72,0:19:27.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於來了個有價值的大素材啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.45,0:19:32.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算命師第一印象是很重要的啊 娜梅
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.10,0:19:36.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直美 改變個髮型會更可愛哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.56,0:19:41.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你們看看我在法國所學的美容技術
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.80,0:19:47.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是那個小子飛奔出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.92,0:19:49.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為什麼那麼忙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.80,0:19:52.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斗澤 最近都不怎麼好相處了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.45,0:19:54.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正也是些…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.02,0:19:58.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是一個不怎麼好的簽呀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.08,0:20:03.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在正·胸的背後一定有個什麼組織 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.08,0:20:05.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先從那裡入手
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.25,0:20:15.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ClonBlade在構造上和WitchBlade是基本相同的  
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.88,0:20:16.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.02,0:20:20.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.03,0:20:23.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.43,0:20:31.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身體狀況怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.10,0:20:33.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.81,0:20:40.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 可以嗎 不會疼的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.40,0:20:45.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 氣死了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.82,0:20:49.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把人當笨蛋 直是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.49,0:20:58.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個人…?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.06,0:21:13.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請讓開
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.98,0:21:20.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,志織
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.69,0:21:25.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看著我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.37,0:21:34.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.17,0:23:14.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽 你的工作看起來很忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.26,0:23:16.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.81,0:23:19.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有長先生和瑪麗子在 不會寂寞的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.43,0:23:23.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 斗澤好像對媽媽有什麼企圖
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.43,0:23:25.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我反對
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.14,0:23:28.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是斗澤也不是媽媽喜歡的類型啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.13,0:23:31.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽適合更帥的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.04,0:23:34.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會緊緊地監視著斗澤的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.16,0:23:36.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽你放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.42,0:23:37.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要努力工作哦
